text: John Watters (1884 - 1961) was a British gymnast. He competed in the men's artistic individual all-around event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1884 births Category:1961 deaths Category:British male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Great Britain Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
